{"tid":2119290,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(叫春post)點 解 疫 症 我 都 要 搵 命 搏 番 工 ？","createTime":"2020-07-22T04:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T10:47:23.000Z","uid":17486,"like":10,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e793e1f6b5012b82ef8968f6e5df9cde4e515dfa","tid":2119290,"uid":17486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:26:41.000Z","msg":"大家有冇得home office? 我老細大前日見成100人確診 ，都無話home office，話睇下呢一兩日點先。 呢兩日平均70人確診， 之後佢話「哦 小左喎 唔係好多確診」。 我心諗， 明明份工都係啲文職office工， 人工又唔係高， 政府都帶頭work from home， 疫情呢排又咁癲， 咁都要搭公共交通工具（地鐵嗰啲放工時間重係好撚多人， 次次搭都好撚驚） 返工放工冒住受感染既風險。 點解要搵條命搏？ 賺又唔係賺得多。最撚慘係， 返工中左無仇報， 勞保又無得claim ， 中左幾麻煩你知架啦。 咁既然我返工都要正常返， 搭車出出入入咁高風險， 點解我唔出去繼續有社交活動，橫掂返工嗰時都有機會中架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=你有home office <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />= 你無home office"},{"pid":"1cda8cf4f20e6a21ee1ee9b00f1c3192bebbb8a3","tid":2119290,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:27:14.000Z","msg":"好過失業啦咁多怨氣咪辭職囉"},{"pid":"65af5c27f79df8377bb804a7c42dfbf7d4fe9db9","tid":2119290,"uid":82532,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://starecat.com/content/wp-content/uploads/god-please-give-me-a-good-reason-for-me-to-get-up-early-and-go-to-work-youre-poor.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstarecat.com%2Fcontent%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fgod-please-give-me-a-good-reason-for-me-to-get-up-early-and-go-to-work-youre-poor.jpg&h=29ecc04a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cbe472e2e3e8ac00c1187e254bbc27f8345cfee","tid":2119290,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:28:13.000Z","msg":"你地home office係一刀切1-5<br />\n定係隔日要返去"},{"pid":"114cecd8e534366667a15c7df3fb583e9c230926","tid":2119290